To build:

0. export RPS_DIR=your rps directory
1. edit setup_rps_env as appropriate
2. source setup_rps_env
3. edit Makefile.conf as appropriate
4. make clean depend all

To run:

0. export RPS_DIR=your rps directory
1. edit setup_rps_env as appropriate
2. source setup_rps_env
3. start_hostloadmeasure.pl
4. start_hostloadpred.pl
5. use loadbufferclient and predbufferclient 

More information to come.  

More information in this technical report: 
  http://reports-archive.adm.cs.cmu.edu/anon/1999/abstracts/99-138.html

Peter A. Dinda
pdinda@cs.nwu.edu
